  "title": "Account Manager",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>To implement sales plans in overall Fire safety products in Singapore.</li>\n  <li>To build market share and establish market awareness.</li>\n  <li>To build good rapport with M&amp;E consultants, M&amp;E contractors and Fire contractors for Commercial and Industrial segments.</li>\n  <li>Able to interpret Fire Alarm /Fire Protection Schematic Diagrams.</li>\n  <li>Possesses good technical knowledge on fire alarm /protection.</li>\n  <li>Must have primarily knowledge of Fire Safety Products and/or Solutions , Spore Standard Code of Practice . Proven track record to generate sales and bring in new clients.</li>\n  <li>Ability to handle pressure and execute multiple tasks simultaneously</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree/Diploma in Business Administration or related industry</li>\n  <li>Previous working experience in Fire Protection Systems</li>\n  <li>Good communication &amp; interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Good presentation skills</li>\n  <li>Computer proficiency in Microsoft Office applications</li>\n</ul>",
